<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>For Brian</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e);
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      max-width: 500px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    h1 {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 15px;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: #ff7aa2;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-style: italic;
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

    button {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: #ff7aa2;
      color: white;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    button:hover {
      background: #ff4f81;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">
  <h1>Hey, Rian? or Brian? 😆</h1>

  <p>
    Semangat kuliahnya ya.  
    Gue cuma stranger yang bakal doain lo biar sukses ke depannya  
    dan lulus tepat waktu. <span class="highlight">Aamiin 🤍</span>
  </p>

  <p>
    I hope someday we can meet at the right time.
  </p>

  <p>
    Untuk sekarang, kita <span class="highlight">senggol-senggolan api dulu 🔥</span>
  </p>

  <p>
    Maybe in another time, kalau lagi ada waktu luang,  
    kita ngobrol lagi kayak awal gue kenal lo.
  </p>

  <div class="footer">
    Salam dari putri Ciledug 👑
  </div>

  <button onclick="alert('Take care yaa 🤍')">Click me</button>
</div>

</body>
</html>
